title: The history of Great Britain being the life and reign of King James the First, relating to what passed from his first access to the crown, till his death / by Arthur Wilson.
author: Wilson, Arthur, 1595-1652.
notes: This copy has been interleaved with plates, of varying dates of engraving, sometime after its original manufacture.
Reproductions of original in the Huntington Library (reel 1110:15) and Corpus Christi College (University of Oxford). Library (reel 2987:21)..
